{"tid":105691,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普 被 曝 已 準 備 參 選 下 屆 總 統","createTime":"2017-02-03T05:46:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-03T06:01:30.000Z","uid":62257,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f9111a0711e41b8b53d1ba6ac54bad869e5b5c72","tid":105691,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T05:46:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.finet.hk/Newscenter/news_detail/58940e46e4b0d1966a2837d9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.finet.hk%2FNewscenter%2Fnews_detail%2F58940e46e4b0d1966a2837d9&d=JC%2BoF4fRaZyKvWcl7nla%2FIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=fb702c69\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.finet.hk/Newscenter/news_detail/58940e46e4b0d1966a2837d9</a><br />\n據英國《每日郵報》2月2日報道，美國總統特朗普已經開始籌劃2020年的第二任期競選，并已籌得1600萬美元。上個月，他還公布了自己的競選口号&mdash;&mdash;&ldquo;讓美國繼續偉大&rdquo;（Keep America Great）。<br />\n根據競選財務報告，特朗普的競選團隊和兩個籌款委員會僅僅在去年12月一個月中，籌款數目就達到1100萬美元。美國政治新聞網站Politico報道稱，在特朗普任總統期間，其位于曼哈頓特朗普大廈的競選總部將保持開放。<br />\n據悉，特朗普在上任還不到1周時，已經為其2020年競選口号&ldquo;讓美國繼續偉大&rdquo;申請商标。《華盛頓郵報》稱，上個月，特朗普在接受采訪中向記者透露了這句口号，随後打斷采訪并找來律師，要求將這個口号申請注冊為商标，之後又繼續接受了采訪。<br />\n特朗普稱，本屆大選的競選口号&ldquo;讓美國再次偉大&rdquo;（Make America Great Again）是2012年總統大選的時候羅姆尼輸給奧巴馬那天他突然想到的。"},{"pid":"8a5d7f400ae620c1ed09bdc78b0a46b3fdbcab91","tid":105691,"uid":18646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T05:48:25.000Z","msg":"參選特首好唔好"},{"pid":"3efe1f2d8caa26c9aa334b883398a5c6e1b623ef","tid":105691,"uid":62691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T05:48:54.000Z","msg":"Donald Trump VS Kanye West，好睇好睇"},{"pid":"435def9febfb5ed5756b6f113a45d01c2725a386","tid":105691,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T05:56:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db4ae89298e442285ba91de9716992b4fa994b74","tid":105691,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T06:01:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}